"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932757-BBC-commentator-Maia-Biginelli-Olympics-Paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  BBCcommentator Leon Taylor pleaded with the judges to penalise Italian diver Maia Biginelli after a 'dangerous' incident at theOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leon Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9660230343733054, \"rank\": 0.03342294579621648, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biginelli came agonisingly close to smashing her head on the diving board after botching an attempt in the women's individual 10 metre platform event.The 21-year-old pulled out all the stops in her bid to reach the final by trying a three-and-a-half somersaults inward dive in the tuck position.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It nearly went horribly wrong, though, with her head coming within a whisker of the board as she attempted to pull off the difficult trick.Taylor, who won a silver medal forTeam GBat the Olympics in 2004, was left shocked by the near-calamity and begged the judges to intervene and punish Biginelli for the 'dangerous' dive.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Judges, you need to do your job now,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You did not do it this morning.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do your job now.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is a dangerous, dangerous dive.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her hair hits the diving board, she should be massively penalised for that.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her hair pretty much hits the board.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What are you watching from your seats?\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What are you watching?\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got a duty of care in this sport to keep athletes safe.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got to penalise.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches, you can see that as well.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Biginelli was awarded a relatively low score of 41.60 on her way to finishing in last place at the end of her semi-final.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She looked sheepish as she made her way out of the pool before chatting with her coaches, who appeared to show her a replay on a small screen.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Novak Djokovic's ex-coach warns Carlos Alcaraz with new retirement prediction  Do not miss:Olympics medal table LIVE: Team GB hot on Australia's heels as USA fight China  Do not miss:Luana Alonso breaks her silence after claims she was 'inappropriate' at Olympics  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wiki